    </item>
    <item>
      <title>调查：一些香港员工希望加薪以放弃混合工作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/hong-kong-staff-demand-6-raise-to-return-to-office-fully</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项调查显示，一些香港员工表示，他们需要加薪才能放弃混合工作安排，这种困境预计将促使更多公司减少办公空间并压低办公室租金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/hong-kong-staff-demand-6-raise-to-return-to-office-fully</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 00:16:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特降价应对中东供应风险，油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯下调所有地区的官方售价后，油价下跌，凸显全球前景恶化，并盖过了对红海紧张局势和利比亚供应中断的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-8</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 23:46:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市在经历了一周的波动后恢复下跌；波音公司坠落：市场休整</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/asia-shares-to-open-flat-as-inflation-data-looms-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市周一跟随亚洲市场走低，而债券则企稳，因为投资者在上周的抛售后重新调整了押注。波音公司在美国盘前交易中暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/asia-shares-to-open-flat-as-inflation-data-looms-markets-wrap</guid>
